    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedAt", c."Description", c."Domain", c."InstructorId", c."IsDeleted", c."Language", c."Level", c."Tags", c."ThumbnailUrl", c."Title", c."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "Courses" AS c
    WHERE c."InstructorId" = @__instructorId_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted")
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS c0
LEFT JOIN "UploadedFiles" AS u ON c0."Id" = u."CourseId"
ORDER BY c0."Id"

    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedAt", c."Description", c."Domain", c."InstructorId", c."IsDeleted", c."Language", c."Level", c."Tags", c."ThumbnailUrl", c."Title", c."UpdatedAt", u."Id" AS "Id0", u."Bio", u."CreatedAt" AS "CreatedAt0", u."Email", u."FullName", u."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", u."PasswordHash", u."PhoneNumber", u."ProfilePictureUrl", u."RefreshToken", u."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt" AS "UpdatedAt0", u."Username"

    INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON c."InstructorId" = u."Id"

) AS s

    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedAt", c."Description", c."Domain", c."InstructorId", c."IsDeleted", c."Language", c."Level", c."Tags", c."ThumbnailUrl", c."Title", c."UpdatedAt", u."Id" AS "Id0", u."Bio", u."CreatedAt" AS "CreatedAt0", u."Email", u."FullName", u."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", u."PasswordHash", u."PhoneNumber", u."ProfilePictureUrl", u."RefreshToken", u."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt" AS "UpdatedAt0", u."Username"
